s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"published\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"2023-06-27T10:16:25.000+02:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"summary\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:393:\"Cette semaine, je vous parle du scandale des panama papers li  WordPress, dun guide et rfrentiel pour crer des sites coconcus, dune extension navigateur pour laccessibilit, dOpquast Start, du travail en collaboration pour le dveloppement de Gutenberg dans Drupal.\nLarticle WOA ! #24 Retours du Wordcamp Europe est apparu en premier sur Agence WordPress Whodunit.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6025:\"\n        \n<p>Cette semaine, je vous parle du scandale des panama papers li  WordPress, dun guide et rfrentiel pour crer des sites coconus, dune extension navigateur pour laccessibilit, dOpquast Start, du travail en collaboration pour le dveloppement de Gutenberg dans Drupal.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jai interrog Marine EVAIN et Jason ROUET, fraichement rentrs du Wordcamp Europe pour lequel ils avaient la grande mission de trouver et grer les sponsors de cet vnement denvergure.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-ecoutez-le-podcast-sur\" data-block-type=\"core\">Ecoutez le podcast sur </h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-5\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/fr/podcast/woa-wordpress-on-air/id1482779414\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/apple-podcasts-e1571142591535.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-66447\" //></a></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/5rEMqG2cyoKYxpTTUAKSPp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/unknown.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-66448\" //></a></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"https://www.deezer.com/fr/show/586602\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/deezer-1024x196.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-66449\" //></a></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow\" data-block-type=\"core\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\" data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"http://podplayer.net/?podId=2447675\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/podcast-addict-for-windows-pc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-66450\" //></a></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile is-image-fill\" style=\"grid-template-columns:31% auto\" data-block-type=\"core\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\" style=\"background-image:url(https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marinejason-1080x833.png);background-position:50% 50%\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1080\" height=\"833\" src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/marinejason-1080x833.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-75932 size-full\" //></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>&nbsp;Jason ROUET :</p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Le Wordcamp Europe, c&#8217;est trois mille personnes, c&#8217;est un million de budget, &#8230; Tout est dcupl par rapport  un Wordcamp local.&#8221;.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Marine EVAIN :</p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;c&#8217;est vraiment chouette aprs neuf mois de travail de voir l&#8217;vnement de faon concrte, c&#8217;est la concrtisation, l&#8217;accomplissement de tout ce travail et avec des relations qui se sont cres.&#8221;</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Erratum de l&#8217;pisode #23 : 27 mai 2003&nbsp;:&nbsp;Matt Mullenweg&nbsp;et&nbsp;Mike Little&nbsp;publient la premire version de WordPress sous la forme dun projet open source cr  partir dun fork du CMS b2/cafelog auparavant fond par le dveloppeur corse&nbsp;Michel Valdrighi.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr data-block-type=\"core\"/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sommaire de l&#8217;pisode :</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p> 01:23 &#8211; Laffaire des panama papers </p>\n\n\n\n<p> 03:00 &#8211; Rfrentiel RGAA </p>\n\n\n\n<p> 04:37 &#8211; Extension navigateur pour laccessibilit </p>\n\n\n\n<p> 06:52 &#8211; Opquast Start </p>\n\n\n\n<p> 08:51 &#8211; 20 000 pour Gutenberg Drupal </p>\n\n\n\n<p> 09:45 &#8211; Composition synchronises </p>\n\n\n\n<p> 10:52 &#8211; Dossier du jour : tre organisateurs volontaires sur le Wordcamp Europe.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-les-liens-de-l-emission\" data-block-type=\"core\">Les liens de l&#8217;mission</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul data-block-type=\"core\">\n<li data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"https://www.temesis.com/blog/laccessibilite-des-sites-francais-en-un-coup-doeil/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ostendo</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"https://ref.greenit.fr/wp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Rfrentiel d&#8217;coconception WordPress</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li data-block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"https://directory.opquast.com/fr/whodunit/83883572/start/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Opquast Start</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-j-attends-vos-retours-avec-impatience\" data-block-type=\"core\">J&#8217;attends vos retours avec impatience&nbsp;!</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:20% auto\" data-block-type=\"core\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/template-carre-1080x1080.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-75791 size-full\" //></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>N&#8217;hsitez pas  laisser un commentaire, a nous fera plaisir et surtout a nous aidera  nous amliorer.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Vous souhaitez intervenir ? Envoyez un mail  eddy@whodunit.fr ou rejoignez-moi sur LinkedIn <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/eddy-boels/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/eddy-boels/</a> pour en discuter.</p>\n</div></div>\n<p>Larticle <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/woa-24-retours-du-wordcamp-europe/\">WOA ! #24 Retours du Wordcamp Europe</a> est apparu en premier sur <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.whodunit.fr\">Agence WordPress Whodunit</a>.</p>\n\n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"\n            \n                                \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Eddy Boels\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:6:\"source\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"\n                    \n                            \n                \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:2:{s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"https://www.whodunit.fr/podca